\tab 
Magick Effects: Light appears to pass through the caster, making him invisible to normal sight; however, he can still be detected by hearing or smell, for example. The effect created by the air nodes is not perfect, and those within 1 yard may make an Obs
erve test to detect a faint \ldblquote shimmering\rdblquote  caused by the invisibility; if passed, they may attack the caster at half WS, or with a spell. Even if the caster i
