Range: Caster\par 
Duration: 1 hour/4 MP\par 
Area of Effect: 12 yard radius sphere\par 
Reagents: Holy water of Shallya*\par 
Resistance: None/WP\par 
\par 
\tab 
All creatures within the area of effect will have their minds filled with images of peace, harmony and tranquillity, and will lose all aggressive thoughts and desires to fight, or otherwise engage in hostile activity.  Since the effect is centered on the 
caster, he may find it difficult to take advantage of others\rquote  inactivity. The caster may move at a Cautious rate while s
till maintaining the spell effects. Those subject to Hatred or Frenzy, or already in combat, may make a WP test to avoid the spell\rquote 
s effects; those in the area of effect may not cast spells to trigger Animosity, Hatred, or Frenzy in others. This spell does not affect creatures immune to psychological reactions, undead, or summoned beings.\par 
