s mind is perceived as an opaque, impenetrable sphere of chaotic magickal energies, waxing and waning at random. Within the area of effect, n
o source of magickal energy can be distinguished, nor can any judgments about the nature of the magickal energy be made.\par 
\tab This spell also blocks perception of the aethyr in line-of-sight which passes through the area of
