\tab Notes: This is the equivalent of dumping aethyrial chaff into magickal radar. Magickal vision is impossible for those within the volume of effect, and magickal vision through the volume of effect is impossible.\par 
\tab See {\i manifest false aethyr} above. {\i Mask aethyr} is most useful in a direct conflict against other magick-sensing or detecting opponents. {\i Manifest false aethyr}
 is most effective for bluffing or stealth against curious, skeptical, or hostile magick-sensing or detecting observers.\par 
